s following.1st Installment: Rs. 1000 at the time of registration of pregnancy. 2nd Installment: Rs 2,000 if they carry out at least one antenatal check-up after six months of pregnancy. 3rd Installment: Rs. 2,000 When the birth of child is registered and the child has received first cycle of vaccines, including BCG, OPV, DPT and hepatitis-B.InstallmentConditionsAmount"}